text: Danai Tsatsou (born 12 July 1980) is a Greek equestrian. She competed in two events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Greek female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Greece Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Athens
